title: Ep 113 - Ignorance is Not Bliss (KNOWLEDGE IS POWER PT 1)
itunes:title: Ep 113 - Ignorance is Not Bliss (KNOWLEDGE IS POWER PT 1)
description:
This is the first part of a four part series titled "Knowledge is Power." People love to use the phrase "Ignorance is Bliss" but in 2016 ignorance is not bliss, it is tragic. With Google and smartphones, ignorance is a decision and that decision to stay ignorant can leave you poor.
